---
import LegalLayout from '@layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
import { type Lang } from '@i18n/utils';
import siteConfig from '@data/site-config.json';

export function getStaticPaths() {
  return [
    { params: { lang: 'es' } },
    { params: { lang: 'en' } }
  ];
}

const { lang } = Astro.params as { lang: Lang };

const content = {
  es: {
    title: 'Politica de Cookies',
    description: 'Informacion sobre las cookies que utilizamos'
  },
  en: {
    title: 'Cookie Policy',
    description: 'Information about the cookies we use'
  }
};
---

<LegalLayout
  title={content[lang].title}
  description={content[lang].description}
  lang={lang}
  updatedAt={new Date('2025-01-15')}
>
  {lang === 'es' ? (
    <>
      <p>
        Usamos cookies para que el sitio funcione correctamente. Aqui explicamos cuales usamos.
      </p>

      <h2>1. Cookies Esenciales</h2>
      <p>Necesarias para el funcionamiento basico del sitio:</p>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Cookie</th>
            <th>Proposito</th>
            <th>Duracion</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>__clerk_*</td>
            <td>Mantener tu sesion iniciada (si tienes cuenta)</td>
            <td>Sesion / 1 ano</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>lang</td>
            <td>Recordar tu idioma preferido</td>
            <td>1 ano</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h2>2. Cookies de Afiliados (Amazon)</h2>
      <p>
        Cuando haces clic en un producto para ir a Amazon, Amazon establece una cookie para
        rastrear la compra y atribuir la comision de afiliado.
      </p>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Cookie</th>
            <th>Proposito</th>
            <th>Duracion</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>Amazon Associates</td>
            <td>Atribucion de comisiones de afiliado</td>
            <td>24 horas</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <p>
        <strong>Nota:</strong> Esta cookie la establece Amazon, no nosotros. No tenemos acceso
        a tu cuenta de Amazon ni a tus datos de compra.
      </p>

      <h2>3. Como Desactivar Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        Puedes configurar tu navegador para rechazar cookies. Ten en cuenta que si lo haces:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>No podras iniciar sesion</li>
        <li>Tu preferencia de idioma no se guardara</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Contacto</h2>
      <p>
        Preguntas: <strong>privacy@bestdeals.com</strong>
      </p>
    </>
  ) : (
    <>
      <p>
        We use cookies to make the site work properly. Here we explain which ones we use.
      </p>

      <h2>1. Essential Cookies</h2>
      <p>Required for basic site functionality:</p>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Cookie</th>
            <th>Purpose</th>
            <th>Duration</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>__clerk_*</td>
            <td>Keep you logged in (if you have an account)</td>
            <td>Session / 1 year</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>lang</td>
            <td>Remember your preferred language</td>
            <td>1 year</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h2>2. Affiliate Cookies (Amazon)</h2>
      <p>
        When you click on a product to go to Amazon, Amazon sets a cookie to track the
        purchase and attribute the affiliate commission.
      </p>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Cookie</th>
            <th>Purpose</th>
            <th>Duration</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>Amazon Associates</td>
            <td>Affiliate commission attribution</td>
            <td>24 hours</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <p>
        <strong>Note:</strong> This cookie is set by Amazon, not us. We have no access
        to your Amazon account or purchase data.
      </p>

      <h2>3. How to Disable Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        You can configure your browser to reject cookies. Note that if you do:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>You won't be able to log in</li>
        <li>Your language preference won't be saved</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions: <strong>privacy@bestdeals.com</strong>
      </p>
    </>
  )}
</LegalLayout>
